record.title: ADJOURNMENT UNTIL 9 A.M. TOMORROW
record.narrative:
ADJOURNMENT UNTIL 9 A.M. TOMORROW -- (Senate - October 03, 2007)

[Page: S12693]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I ask unanimous consent that the Senate stand adjourned under the previous order.

record.narrative: There being no objection, the Senate, at 7:35 p.m., adjourned until Thursday, October 4, 2007, at 9 a.m.
